       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CALCULO-INTERESES.
       AUTHOR. KATA LEGACY2MODERN.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DATOS-INTERES.
           05  WS-CAPITAL          PIC 9(09)V99.
           05  WS-TASA-INTERES     PIC V999.
           05  WS-PLAZO-DIAS       PIC 9(03).
       01  WS-RESULTADO-INTERES.
           05  WS-INTERES-GANADO   PIC 9(07)V99.
           05  WS-TOTAL-CON-INTERES PIC 9(09)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-PROCESO.
           DISPLAY "CALCULANDO INTERESES MENSUALES".
           
           MOVE 50000 TO WS-CAPITAL.           
           MOVE 0.15 TO WS-TASA-INTERES.

           COMPUTE WS-INTERES-GANADO = WS-CAPITAL * WS-TASA-INTERES.
           COMPUTE WS-TOTAL-CON-INTERES = WS-CAPITAL + WS-INTERES-GANADO.

           DISPLAY "CAPITAL INICIAL: " WS-CAPITAL.
           DISPLAY "TASA APLICADA: " WS-TASA-INTERES.
           DISPLAY "INTERES GANADO: " WS-INTERES-GANADO.
           DISPLAY "TOTAL FINAL: " WS-TOTAL-CON-INTERES.

           STOP RUN.
